summary: The Roaring Kitteh Collection - The Roaring Kitteh Collection is a set of 5555 unique NFT’s brought to life from a manifestation of Keith Gill as a cat. A cat who does not know they are one, but proudly states 'I am not a cat, I am kitteh'. The collection provides a gateway to membership into The Roaring Family of tokens, to be utilize within the ecosystem built around it. The story of The Roaring Family has already begun as the games of kitteh begin to unfold.
